Class RequestScopeSuperBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.RequestScopeSuperBean

  • public class RequestScopeSuperBean
extends Object
    This is a replacement for the RequestScopeApplicationContext which turned out to be too slow. It is hideous and probably very confusing however it will allow me to keep things working whilst I refactor.
